## COLOR BLINDNESS

### Most common types:
| Type | % Men | Confuses |
|---|---|---|
| Deuteranopia (green) | 6% | Green ‚Üî Red |
| Protanopia (red) | 2% | Red ‚Üî Green |
| Tritanopia (blue) | 0.01% | Blue ‚Üî Yellow |
| Achromatopsia (total) | 0.003% | Everything ‚Üí gray |

### RULES:
- Red and green TOGETHER need an extra differentiator (icon, pattern, label)
- Charts: Use patterns (lines, dots) in addition to color
- Status: ‚úì check + green, ‚úï cross + red, ‚ö† triangle + yellow
- Test with color blindness simulator (Figma plugin: "Color Blind")

